data.description:
CALL AGENT for all questions-Angela-760-453-6758.
Beautiful Rosetta Canyon home! Builder upgrades abound including granite countertops, a large kitchen island, upgraded appliances and cozy fireplace. Upstairs bonus room is ideal for office space, pool table or rec room area. Spacious master bedroom includes en suite bathroom with soaking tub and tons of natural light. Spacious 3 car garage is great for all your toys or extra storage. Private back yard is perfect to create your own entertaining landscape with a built in horse shoe pit! Seller may give concession depending on offer.
data.whatILove: Quiet neighborhood, perfectly located near all shopping, dining and easy freeway access. Beautiful 216 ACRE park was recently added offering full sized CIF football/Soccer field with LED sportsfield lighting, concession stand, jogging trail, 1.25 acre dog park, community garden. GREAT PLACE TO CALL HOME!
